-- Camtek Rises Most in Week After Orders Valued at $3.5 Million
-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 2012-03-26T11:14:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-26/camtek-rises-most-in-week-after-orders-valued-at-3-5-million.html
  Camtek Ltd. (CAMT)  advanced the most in
more than a week after the maker of optical-inspection systems
said it received orders valued at more than $3.5 million.  The  shares  advanced 3.3 percent, the most since March 15,
to 9.2 shekels at 12:06 p.m. in  Tel Aviv .  To contact the reporter on this story:
